structure.unit: FEES AND COMPENSATION OF PUBLIC OFFICERS AND EMPLOYEES

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 159, sec. 6, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 162, sec. 3, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 1. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 71, secs. 1, 2, 3, and 4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Mileage allowance to officers serving papers.
